DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-15T10:15:00&endDate=2026-03-16T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Sunday 15 March\, from 1015\, a reduced service operates. Trains operate every 30 minutes between London Fields and Chingford\, every hour between London Fields and Cheshunt\, and every hour between London Fields and Enfield Town. There will be no service to/from Liverpool Street\, Bethnal Green and Cambridge Heath all day. No GREATER ANGLIA services call at Hackney Downs or Seven Sisters all day.
